[One must wonder whether this outbreak will have spread further
beyond France with the dispersion of pupils to other countries at the
end of the school year.

An interactive map of the Cote d'Or, France, is available at:
<http://encarta.msn.com/map_701511873/cote-dor.html>.
- Mod.CP

